    "body": "### Description\n\nI have set the highlight of NormalFloat and FlaotBorder to fit my background color(I am using gruvbox colorscheme), as follows:\r\n```lua\r\nvim.cmd(\"hi NormalFloat guibg=#32302F\")\r\nvim.cmd(\"hi FloatBorder guibg=#32302F guifg=#F2E2C3\")\r\n```\r\nThen when my cursor is right after the parenthesis of a function in the insert mode, the lsp float window shows up, like this:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1442\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/assets/64594442/823d5706-33f8-4c7f-a97f-1ae24b3ff8e7\">\r\n\r\nI want the window to be bordered, so after checking the wiki I set\r\n```lua\r\nlocal lspconfig = require(\"lspconfig\")\r\nlocal handlers = {\r\n\t[\"textDocument/hover\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.hover, { border = \"rounded\"}),\r\n\t[\"textDocument/signatureHelp\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.signature_help, { border = \"rounded\"}),\r\n}\r\nlspconfig.pyright.setup({\r\n\thandlers = handlers,\r\n})\r\nlspconfig.lua_ls.setup({\r\n\thandlers = handlers,\r\n})\r\n```\r\nBut it seems not working, what should I do? Any help would be appreciated.\r\n\r\nBtw, when I invoke `vim.lsp.buf.hover` in the normal mode, there is a bordered float window shown beside my cursor, which is what I also want when writing a function in the insert mode.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"1252\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/neovim/nvim-lspconfig/assets/64594442/a8067ac8-ef23-4ce1-b1a4-ed83159cbdba\">\n\n### Neovim version\n\nNVIM v0.9.1\r\nBuild type: Release\r\nLuaJIT 2.1.0-beta3\n\n### Nvim-lspconfig version\n\n`a981d44`\n\n### Operating system and version\n\nmacOS 12.6.7\n\n### Affected language servers\n\nall\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nSame as description.\n\n### Actual behavior\n\nBorder of lsp float window disappears when writing function in insert mode.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nBorder of lsp float window shows when writing function in normal mode, like when vim.lsp.buf.hover is invoked.\n\n### Minimal config\n\n```Lua\nvim.cmd(\"hi NormalFloat guibg=#32302F\")\r\nvim.cmd(\"hi FloatBorder guibg=#32302F guifg=#F2E2C3\")\r\nlocal lspconfig = require(\"lspconfig\")\r\nlocal handlers = {\r\n\t[\"textDocument/hover\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.hover, { border = \"rounded\"}),\r\n\t[\"textDocument/signatureHelp\"] = vim.lsp.with(vim.lsp.handlers.signature_help, { border = \"rounded\"}),\r\n}\r\nlspconfig.pyright.setup({\r\n\thandlers = handlers,\r\n})\r\nlspconfig.lua_ls.setup({\r\n\thandlers = handlers,\r\n})\n```\n\n\n### LSP log\n\nhttps://gist.github.com/yizhenAllen/7f724d12a5cafe29d307b4068eaf08da",
